一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=7fe06b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"c40b7c2ffb02b6fda26687be5cfbd9fa4450d0ef","tid":2477942,"uid":347099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27aa12510f146ca36e434eb770ab243491c6a33c","tid":2477942,"uid":364843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18be3086d7604fef15fafa76e340db38284569e5","tid":2477942,"uid":347099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a9ca4ee8ebb326d6faf4b19c00b7cca81ae6511","tid":2477942,"uid":364843,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"同你一樣咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太多負面事情發生後，已經冇乜力企返身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"我都係中學畢業之後就發生好多事，身體又有病痛，睇醫生又遇過態度差既醫生搞到我每次諗返起嗰次經歷都會覺得好唔開心，覺得自己係咪好阻掟，連醫生都唔鐘意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唯一嘅願望就係希望自己同身邊既人都健康就夠了。btw 睇你既post你話舌頭有白斑要做手術，而家無事嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"切咗又無事了，報告話如果唔切會變cancer"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"我舌頭側邊好似都有啲長期潰瘍..尤其食辣野會痛，想請問你知唔知應該睇咩科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0f2270e0032d7ced4fe2629fd4f803e9cbe61c","tid":2477942,"uid":23495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"睇樓豬舊post <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" cla